{"tid":840582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏] 人民日報海外版指美國任性　或令全球落入「衰退陷阱」","createTime":"2018-09-29T01:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T05:01:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ab4063e50c6ed7e2170866e4d31d6918598c73","tid":840582,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"人民日報海外版指美國任性　或令全球落入「衰退陷阱」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420533-20180929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420533-20180929.htm&d=HfsGu98mWmxfAKfnpc4x7U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3c51587a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420533-20180929.htm&h=e160d9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420533-20180929.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n人民日報海外版發表文章，批評美國任性，指美國自稱的「光榮與夢想」價值觀，正經受自己發起的貿易戰嚴峻考驗。<br />\n<br />\n文章指美國破壞多邊貿易，把文明的規則一腳踢開；又說當年推動建立多邊貿易體系的是美國，如今破壞這個體系的同樣是美國，質疑美國有無契約精神。<br />\n<br />\n人民日報海外版指美國政府阻礙國際貿易，會對世界經濟復蘇造成負面影響，為了遏制美國的貿易保護主義行為，其他國家不得不採取反制措施，這樣將導致全球經貿秩序混亂，損害各國企業和民眾，令全球經濟落入「衰退陷阱」。"},{"pid":"400020e3a487ca2183ea1eeed0cbf3eefd345a8b","tid":840582,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"佔中仆街令香港經濟陷入衰退<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672d0bbdb33f2586b195d506ea09c6ed9d310a97","tid":840582,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"400020e3a487ca2183ea1eeed0cbf3eefd345a8b","tid":840582,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"佔中仆街令香港經濟陷入衰退<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"佔中鈎結外國勢力<br />\n私通美國<br />\n透露國家機密<br />\n令美國有機可乘<br />\n制定對華策略<br />\n正漢奸"},{"pid":"df7377e7de3859770ad85fbe04743eaf816cabad","tid":840582,"uid":41245,"l